Description:
Awakened doomsday, death, the worst of the legendary Four Horsemen, hits the road in order to restore humanity and clear the name of his brother. Along the way, the rider learns that there are things worse than the world's Apocalypse, and that the ancient feud is likely to endanger the whole of Creation ...

The events of the second part develops parallel to the events of the first. The war is still locked up in prison, and now we have to learn the history of the second horseman of the Apocalypse - Death. He tries to understand the conspiracy between hell and paradise for the right to possession of the earth and to find and punish those who framed war.
